<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css' />
    <script src="/bootstrap/js/jquery-1.11.0.js"></script>
    <script src="/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <style>
        html,body{width:100%;height:100%;}
        body{background: url(../img/bg2.jpg) no-repeat;background-size:100% 100%}
        .jumbotron{background: url(../img/bg3.jpg) no-repeat;background-size:100%}
        .navbar{background: url(../img/bg3.jpg) no-repeat;background-size:100%}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    	<!-- 引入头部文件 -->
    	<%- include("./header.ejs",{name:"注册页面",isShow:false})%>	
        
    	<div class="container" style="padding-bottom:40px;">
    		<form method="post" action="/register">
    		  <div class="form-group">
    		    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">请填写姓名</label>
    		    <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="昵称" name="username">
    		  </div>
    		  <div class="form-group">
    		    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">请填写邮箱</label>
    		    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" placeholder="邮箱" name="email">
    		  </div>
    		  <div class="form-group">
    		    <label for="exampleInputPassword1">请填写密码</label>
    		    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="密码" name="password">
    		  </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputPassword1">个人介绍</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="密码" name="introduce">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputPassword1">职务</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="密码" name="job">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputPassword1">获奖情况</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="密码" name="win">
              </div>
    		  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-info">点击注册</button>
    		</form>
            
    		<%if(isShow){%>
    			<p style="color:red;">该用户名已存在，快换一个吧</p>
    		<%}%>
            
    	</div>

    	<div class="container">
    		<div class="jumbotron">
    		  <h2>欢迎使用本网站,祝您使用愉快。。。</h2>
    		  <p>本网站，是全世界最好最大的网站,是的你没有听错...</p>
    		  <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-info" href="/login" role="button">已注册，去登陆</a></p>
    		</div>
    	</div>

  </body>
</html>